                <p>See commentary at <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr081900</ref>.</p>
                <p>The father's name was abbreviated either for <foreign xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>Εὐκ</abbr><ex>λεῦς</ex></expan></foreign> or
